none

### Acceptance criteria
- Given POST /posts/1/like, when toggled, then returns { liked: true/false, likesCount: N }
- Given a user likes a post, then a notification is created for the post owner (not self)
- Given a user follows another, then a 'follow' notification is created
- Given GET /notifications, returns notifications with actor info, sorted by newest first
- Given GET /notifications/unread-count, returns { count: N }
- Given PATCH /notifications/read-all, marks all user's notifications as read
- Given GET /feed/world, posts now include likesCount and isLiked fields

### Files to modify
- `backend/node-services/api-server/src/services/database.ts` — migration 016, 7 new DB methods, update feed queries
